title: Team LF Jungler Main Only
body:
We are currently in need of a Jungler who can play from 7pm-10pm / 5pm-10pm Weekdays/Weekends.

Current Team Ranks: Our team is Silver 5.

Top: Gold 5
Mid: Plat 5
Jungler: N/A
ADC: Gold 2
Support: Silver 2

The requirements to join:

Must be Plat - Gold - Silver
Be willing to play Tank/Hypercarry Jungler Champions
Team-Speak 3 - MUST HAVE A MIC, this is an absolute must. (We're a pretty laid-back group)

Note, not everyone will be online most days. So there will be days where we all wont be online, Working late, Having a break ect.

If you would like to be Apart of a Team Environment, Please Add me on the league of legends Game Client. (Remember, Jungler mains only) {{champion:154}}
